mksinterface.mksitem.src

Class Mksinterface_mksfield

  • java.lang.Object
    • mksinterface.mksitem.src.Mksinterface_mksfield

  • public class Mksinterface_mksfield
extends java.lang.Object
    This special field class represents a full field of an item in Integrity. You are able to feed the class with an "Field" element which is given directly from Integrity or feed it with your own parameters. Internal the fields will be saved with their correct types and values.
    Author:
    ckaltenboeck
